  "body": "There is a startup  issue on the docker-1.13.x branch after commit 595e75c212d19a81d2b808a518fe1afc1391dad5\r\n\r\nWith a /run directory cleared by a reboot:\r\n\r\n```\r\n/ # /usr/bin/containerd\r\nFATA[0000] can't create unix socket /run/containerd/containerd.sock: listen unix /run/containerd/containerd.sock: bind: no such file or directory \r\n```\r\n\r\nDoing a `mkdir /run/containerd` before starting containerd fixes the problem. ",
